[Student "S"]
{The bidding has been as shown.   

You just scrape 7 points together. With your 4-card Major that's enough for a Negative Double. So you double and partner jumps to 2\S. What is your bid? 

Partner's jump is inviting but it takes more than just a simple jump to get you excited with this junk. Even though partner has 16-18 points you pass.}

